CNA map PDF
-----------
File: CNA-CB-Map-v1.4.pdf

The map is derived from *The Campaign for North Africa: The Desert War
1940-43*, published by Simulations Publications, Inc. (SPI) in 1979.
Current rights are believed to be held by White Box Games (© 2022).
Bundled here so the rendering pipeline works out of the box.

Counter art (images/)
---------------------
The unit counter SVG and PNG files in `images/` originate from the
community-maintained Vassal module for The Campaign for North Africa.
Vassal itself is open-source software released under the LGPL; the
module's counter art is contributed by the wargaming community.

